Uses of Interface
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content.Group

  • Packages that use Group 
    Package Description
    it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content
    Provides classes defining the message contents used for interacting with the group service.

    • Uses of Group in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content

      Classes in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content that implement Group 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Cancel
      The Cancel class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to cancel a member from a group.
      class  Deregister
      The Deregister class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to remove a specific group.
      class  Link
      The Link class defines a task request, sent from an actor space service provider, for asking a remote actor space service provider to add the reference associated with the local group to the references of the remote group.
      class  Register
      The Register class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to register a specific group.
      class  Signup
      The Signup class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to add one or more actors to a group.
      class  Unlink
      The Unlink class defines a task request, sent from an actor space service provider, for asking a remote actor space service provider to remove the local group reference from the destinations of the remote group, because there are not more subscribers to the local group.
